extends _includes/layout.pug

block content
    header
        h1 I am #{site.author}
            span A software developer

    main
        p This is a work in progress. Have some cat ipsum and a sleeping bunny!

        p Gnaw the corn cob. Meow go back to sleep owner brings food and water tries to pet on head, so scratch get sprayed by water because bad cat and sometimes switches in french and say "miaou" just because well why not scratch me there. Kitty scratches couch bad kitty spend all night ensuring people don't sleep all day kitty power play riveting piece on synthesizer keyboard and your pillow is now my pet bed.

        figure.bunny
            input#bunny.bunny__state(type="checkbox")
            label.bunny__container(for="bunny")
                img.bunny__image(alt="A sleeping bunny" src="static/images/bunny.png")

    footer
        dl.footer__links
            dt.footer__icon.footer__icon--github
            dd
                a(href="https://github.com/" + site.github) @#{site.github}

            dt.footer__icon.footer__icon--twitter
            dd
                a(href="https://twitter.com/" + site.twitter) @#{site.twitter}